on between RPs.\r\n- MBGP (Multiprotocol BGP) used to exchange routing information for interdomain RPF checking.\r\n- SSM &amp; other topics\r\n- Deploying multicast in a multi-vendor environment ',2006,'October','Y','/var/www/html/data/2006/','2020-12-18 17:10:06','Administrative Account','2006-08-10 23:07:38','admin@ws.edu.isoc.org','N',NULL,'no','no',0,0,13.753980,100.501442),(183,6,'APRICOT 2008','2008-02-20','2008-02-29','http://www.apricot.net/','http://www.twnic.net.tw','TW','Taipei','Asia/Australia/Pacific','','','English','','','','TBA','APIA Secretariat','apia-sec@apia.org','',2008,'February','Y','/var/www/html/data/2008/','2020-12-18 17:10:12','Administrative Account','2006-09-07 00:33:15','pfs@cisco.com','N',NULL,'no','no',0,0,25.047760,121.531853),(184,6,'APRICOT 2009','2009-02-18','2009-02-27','http://www.apricot.net/','','PH','Manila','Asia/Australia/Pacific','','','English','','','','','APIA Secretariat','apia-sec@apia.org','APRICOT 2009 will be hosted by ASTI.',2009,'February','Y','/var/www/html/data/2009/','2020-12-18 17:10:20','Administrative Account','2007-09-12 04:10:53','pfs@cisco.com','N',NULL,'no','no',0,0,14.604200,120.982201),(185,6,'APRICOT 2010','2010-02-23','2010-03-05','http://www.apricot.net/','','MY','Kuala Lumpur','Asia/Australia/Pacific','','','English','','','','Kuala Lumpur Convention Centre','APIA Secretariat','apia-sec@apia.org','',2010,'February','Y','/var/www/html/data/2010/','2020-12-18 17:10:26','Administrative Account','2009-03-03 22:23:56','pfs@cisco.com','N',NULL,'no','no',0,0,3.141200,101.686531),(186,6,'WALC 2006','2006-07-24','2006-07-29','http://www.walc2006.ula.ve/','http://www.walc2006.ula.ve/infor/inscrip.php','ec','Quito','Latin America/Caribbean islands','North America','','Spanish','Portuguese','English','','','','','El prop&oacute;sito de estos talleres consiste en contribuir a satisfacer las necesidades de capacitaci&oacute;n de t&eacute;cnicos y profesionales provenientes de pa&iacute;ses de Am&eacute;rica La