www.lacnic.net/en/eventos/lacnicxii/registrarse.html\r\n\r\nDetailed information about the meeting, agenda, accommodation,\r\nregistration and general information is available from the meeting\r\nwebsite at:\r\n\r\nhttp://www.lacnic.net/en/eventos/lacnicxii/index.html\r\n\r\nFor any questions regarding the event or for those interested in\r\nsponsoring LACNIC XII, please go to:\r\n\r\nhttp://www.lacnic.net/en/eventos/lacnicxii/patrocinadores.html\r\n\r\nor contact meeting@lacnic.net requesting information.\r\n\r\n\r\nSincerely,\r\n\r\nMember Services and Communications\r\nLACNIC ',2009,'May','Y','/var/www/html/data/2009/','2020-12-18 17:28:07','Lucy Lynch','2009-02-11 13:20:39','admin@ws.edu.isoc.org','N',NULL,'no','no',0,0,8.993600,-79.519730),(355,457,'AfriNIC-9','2008-11-22','2008-11-28','http://meeting.afrinic.net/afrinic9/','http://www.afrinic.net/meeting/afrinic-9/registration.htm','mu','Pointe Aux Piments','Africa','Global','','English','French','','','Le M√©ridien Ile Maurice','Meeting Coordinator','meeting@afrinic.net','\r\nAfriNIC invites you to attend AfriNIC-9, the 9th Open Policy Meeting to be held in Mauritius. Le M&eacute;ridien Ile Maurice, at Village Hall Lane, Pointe Aux Piments, Mauritius. The meeting is open to everyone and provide an excellent opportunity to take part in Internet policy discussions.\r\n\r\nLe M&eacute;ridien Ile Maurice is located 60 kilometers from the island‚Äôs international airport and only 15 kilometers from the island&#039;s hub, Grand Baie, known for its shopping, restaurants, bars, and nightlife. The island‚Äôs capital, Port-Louis, a bustling centre of business and entertainment, is only 15 kilometers from Le M&eacute;ridien Ile Maurice. \r\n',2008,'November','Y','/var/www/html/data/2008/','2020-12-18 17:28:13','Adiel Akplogan','2008-10-23 20:54:06','admin@ws.edu.isoc.org','N',NULL,'no','no',0,0,-20.080280,57.506390),(357,6,'19th Asian School on Computer Science','2008-11-16','2008-11-17','http://www.interlab.ait.ac.th/a