TTN), an initiative to build a world-wide \r\nopen source infrastructure to facilitate a \r\npublic Internet of Things. TTN operates by \r\nallowing users to share the access to \r\ngateways. We think NRENs in the region \r\nshould play a leading role in hosting this \r\ninfrastructure. As TTN allows for low-\r\nbandwidth communications over long \r\ndistances, it can facilitate the deployment of \r\napplications relevant to East African \r\ncountries.\r\n \r\nTopics:\r\n√¢‚Ç¨¬¢ Wireless solutions for IoT;\r\n√¢‚Ç¨¬¢ LoRa and LoRaWAN protocols;\r\n√¢‚Ç¨¬¢ Prototyping of sensor boards;\r\n√¢‚Ç¨¬¢ Planning and deployment of a LPWAN \r\nnetwork;\r\n√¢‚Ç¨¬¢ Collection and visualization of the data.',2020,'February','Y','/var/www/sites/data/2020/','2020-12-18 19:59:22','Administrative Account','2020-01-23 17:11:41',NULL,'N',NULL,'no','no',0,0,0.339660,32.564140),(1897,959,'M3AAWG 49th General Meeting','2020-06-08','2020-06-11','https://www.m3aawg.org/upcoming-meetings','','US','','North America','','','English',NULL,NULL,'','Virtual Event','M3AAWG Contact Us Page','','Please use our contact us form for any \r\nquestions regarding this event. \r\nhttps://www.m3aawg.org/contact-us',2020,'June','Y','/var/www/sites/data/2020/','2020-08-17 19:12:42','Marcia Molina','2020-04-14 21:41:50',NULL,'N',NULL,'no','no',0,1,0.000000,0.000000),(1885,954,'UGNOG','2020-10-12','2020-10-13','To be uploaded soon','','Ug','Kampala','Africa','','','English',NULL,NULL,'','Kampala','Isabel Odida','isabel.odida@gmail.com','The website link shall be uploaded in the \r\nsoon.',2020,'October','Y','/var/www/sites/data/2020/','2020-12-18 19:59:29','Isabel Odida','2020-02-03 11:13:31',NULL,'N',NULL,'no','no',0,0,0.316280,32.582191),(1886,804,'ARIN 47','2021-04-12','2021-04-14','http://www.arin.net','','US','','North America','','','English','','','','','Melissa Goodwin','meetings@arin.net','',2021,'April','Y','/var/www/sites/data/2021/','2021-02-11 03:23:29','Melissa Goodwin','2021-02-10 19:20:33','mgo